arStrings.szText: “Where did the Sightless Eye come from?”
It's a relic from when the world was young. For many years, an order of rogues called the Sisters of the Sightless Eye kept it safe.
Not sure how they lost hold of it, but I’ve heard the Sisters are not as strong as they once were.
Knowledge of their craft has spread to others, but most rogues you see these days are not true members of the order.
